<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: SMB USA Plus (SMB2 USA)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=11590&amp;p=136001#p136001"><![CDATA[
Okay. I've made 2 fixes.<br /><br />1) Made it so that the player starts off with five lives, just like in the SNES Allstars version. ($04ED appears to be the lives counter. I traced code and found an LDA #$03 STA $04ED. ROM location is 0x1E425)<br /><br />2) Made the game to have five continues, instead of two. (Counter for this is found at RAM $05C5)<br /><br />SMB USA original ROM CRC16 = DE2A<br /><br />--<em><strong>ShaneM</strong></em><br /><br />SEE BELOW FOR FINAL DOWNLOAD<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=5262">ShaneM</a> — Mon Nov 03, 2014 10:00 pm</p><hr />
